PortSystem 1.0
name		libgnomemm
version		2.0.1
description	libgnomemm provides C++ wrappers for libgnome.
long_description        ${description}
maintainers	gnome-darwinports@opendarwin.org
categories	gnome
platforms	darwin 
homepage	http://www.gtkmm.org/
master_sites    sourceforge:gtkmm
